        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"z05-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z05-section dark z05-gallery-section\"><div class=\"z05-wrap\"><div class=\"z05-gallery-head\"><p class=\"z05-kicker\">Listening Notes</p><h2>What you notice when it is in hand</h2><p class=\"z05-gallery-lead\">A few close looks at the parts that change daily listening: the AuAg faceplates, the physical TwinCore switch, the cable system, and the tips that keep the seal honest.</p></div><div class=\"z05-gallery-grid\"><figure class=\"feature\"><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-forged-carbon-faceplate-hero.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg main faceplate hero image\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>AuAg faceplates</b><span>Gold on one side, silver on the other. It is the kind of finish you keep turning under the light before the first track even starts.</span></figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-twincore-switch-closeup.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg TwinCore switch close-up\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>TwinCore switch</b><span>A real switch for real mood changes: more body when you want to sink in, more bite when you want to listen closer.</span></figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-swappable-cable-terminations.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg cable and swappable terminations\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>Cable kit</b><span>Phone, dongle, DAP, desktop chain. The included terminations cover the sources most of us actually rotate through.</span></figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-liquidmorph-accessory-tray.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg LiquidMorph eartip tray\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>LiquidMorph tips</b><span>Tip rolling is not decoration here. A better seal means steadier bass, cleaner center image, and less fiddling mid-album.</span></figcaption></figure></div></div></section></div><style>.z05-gallery-section{padding:56px 0;background:#050607}.z05-gallery-head{text-align:left;max-width:920px}.z05-gallery-section h2{