        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"z05-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z05-section z05-fitment-section\"><div class=\"z05-wrap\"><div class=\"z05-fitment-head\"><div><p class=\"z05-kicker\">Fitment</p><h2>A universal fit that still feels settled</h2></div><p>The best tuning falls apart if the shell keeps shifting. Z05 AuAg keeps the body compact, routes the cable over-ear, and lets the tip do the sealing work.</p></div><div class=\"z05-fitment-showcase\"><figure class=\"z05-fitment-image\"><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-male-fitment.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Adult male wearing Z05 AuAg universal in-ear monitor with over-ear cable\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>Real-world fit check</b><span>The cable takes the strain, the shell sits close, and the tip keeps the bass from wandering.</span></figcaption></figure><div class=\"z05-fitment-panel\"><article><span>Over-ear route</span><h3>Cable stays put</h3><p>Less tug at the shell when you move, sit, or swap sources.</p></article><article><span>Compact body</span><h3>No custom mold needed</h3><p>A small universal body that sits naturally instead of trying to fill the whole ear.</p></article><article><span>Seal support</span><h3>LiquidMorph tips</h3><p>LiquidMorph tips help lock in bass pressure and center image.</p></article></div></div></div></section></div><style>.z05-fitment-section{background:#f4f1ea;color:#111}.z05-fitment-head{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,.95fr) minmax(360px,.72fr);gap:34px;align-items:end}.z05-fitment-head h2{max-width:760px;font-size:clamp(36px,4.8vw,66px)}.z05-fitment-head>p{margin:0;color:#302b25;font-size:17px;line-height:1.62}.z05-fitment-showcase{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1.18fr) minmax(320px,.82fr);gap:22px;align-items:stretch;margin-top:34px}.z05-fitment-image{margin:0;position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:#080808;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.16);padding:14px;min-height:0}.z05-fitment-image img{display:block;width:100%;height:auto;aspect-ratio:16/10