        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"z05-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z05-section z05-accessory-section\"><div class=\"z05-wrap\"><div class=\"z05-accessory-head\"><div><p class=\"z05-kicker\">Signal Chain Ready</p><h2>One cable, the sources most of us actually use</h2></div><p>No one wants to buy a new cable on day one. Z05 AuAg ships with the paths that cover the usual rotation: phone, dongle, DAP, and desktop stack.</p></div><div class=\"z05-accessory-showcase\"><figure class=\"z05-accessory-image\"><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-complete-package-flatlay.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg complete kit with cable, monitors, and swappable 3.5mm, 4.4mm, and Type-C terminations\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>The usual source rotation</b><span>Monitors, cable, and terminations in one kit, so the first listen is not delayed by accessory hunting.</span></figcaption></figure><div class=\"z05-accessory-panel\"><article><span>Portable</span><h3>3.5mm + Type-C</h3><p>Quick analog or digital listening when the phone or laptop is the source.</p></article><article><span>Balanced</span><h3>4.4mm ready</h3><p>For DAPs and compact DAC/amps when you want the balanced output.</p></article><article><span>Monitor side</span><h3>2-pin detachable</h3><p>A familiar monitor-side connection for long-term cable flexibility.</p></article><div class=\"z05-accessory-cta\"><a class=\"z05-btn\" href=\"/cart/add?id={{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}&quantity=1\">Buy Now</a></div></div></div></div></section></div><style>.z05-accessory-section{background:#f4f1ea;color:#111}.z05-accessory-head{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,.95fr) minmax(360px,.72fr);gap:34px;align-items:end}.z05-accessory-head h2{max-width:760px;font-size:clamp(36px,4.8vw,66px)}.z05-accessory-head>p{margin:0;color:#302b25;font-size:17px;line-height:1.62}.z05-accessory-showcase{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1.18fr) minmax(320px,.82fr);gap:22px;align-items:stretch;margin-top:34px}.z05